        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: 6 turns</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 30&rsquo;</strong></p>\n<p>The caster can communicate with one type of animal within range when the spell is cast.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Type of animal:</strong> Ordinary animals or giant versions of ordinary animals may be targeted.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Questions: </strong>The caster can ask questions of and receive answers from animals of the chosen kind, although the spell doesn&rsquo;t make animals any more friendly or cooperative than normal (a reaction roll may be required).</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Services: </strong>If an animal is friendly toward the caster, it may perform some favour or service.</p>",
